org.example

Class ValueReferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.example.ValueReferences

  • public class ValueReferences
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to describe a data request for comparison. Create an object with a key that is the name of the data requested and a Collection of sensor/s to obtain that data for comparison. JSON obtained {"valueName" : ["comparator"] }
